# ===========================================================================
# 301 redirects — collapse legacy ".html" URLs into the clean canonical URLs.
# Format: Cloudflare Pages / Netlify  (place this file in the deploy root).
#
# NETLIFY USERS: append "!" to each "301" (e.g. "301!") to force the redirect
# over the existing .html file. Cloudflare Pages does not need the "!".
#
# NOTE: blog POST URLs are intentionally NOT redirected — they canonicalize
# WITH ".html". Only main pages + the one duplicate post are redirected.
# ===========================================================================

